            <a:pPr indent="0" marL="0"><a:buNone/></a:pPr>
            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1100" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="EF4444"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t xml:space="preserve">Q: “When can we go live with comp?” </a:t></a:r>
            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1100" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="CADCFC"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>Pipeline is production-ready. Comp go-live requires: correction workflow, clawback policy, dispute process, and CFO sign-off. Open questions documented in product spec §11.</a:t></a:r>
          </a:p>
        </p:txBody>
