            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1100" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="EF4444"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t xml:space="preserve">Q: “What would you do differently?” </a:t></a:r>
            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1100" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="CADCFC"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>Start with segment-specific ramp windows in v1. Instrument engagement quality (alerts acted on, policies deployed) from day one, not as a v2 afterthought.</a:t></a:r>
